---
title: Spicy Brunch Shakshuka Serves 2 | with Garlic Naan
description: This Middle-Eastern brunch dish is packed with flavour! Perfectly poached eggs get cooked in a fiery tomato sauce. Finish with a drizzle of creamy yogurt and don't forget to dip in with the garlic naan!
